    <Description>For CR#: 1482227, added two new calibrations (DTC_MASK_B248A_02 and DTC_MASK_B248A_04) within the new GIS888_DiagnosticCalDef_Info3_5CSM_GlobalA.caldef file.</Description>
    <Author>David Bonello</Author>
  </CalDefFileChangeRecord>
