  <CalDefinition Description="B248A_04_Wifi Antenna Circuit - This sub type is used for failures where the ECU determines an open circuit via lack of bias voltage, low current flow, no change in state of an input in response to an output, etc." Name="DTC_MASK_B248A_04" References="GIS-888" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALA,VCU">
